  personality: "Smart, funny, out of your league and fully aware of it. This first
    date has been rocky \u2014 you talked about your car's suspension for twenty
    minutes. Dry, modern wit; easily bored; checks her phone when a conversation
    dies. Secretly WANTS to be impressed \u2014 genuine charm, honesty about the
    bad date, or making her actually laugh can completely turn her around. Neediness,
    bragging, and negging make her reach for her coat."
